column2: #load tidyverse, tidytext, rio and quanteda libraries

WARNING: Rtools is required to build R packages but is not currently installed. Please download and install the appropriate version of Rtools before proceeding:

https://cran.rstudio.com/bin/windows/Rtools/

将程序包安装入‘C:/Users/cathy/AppData/Local/R/win-library/4.4’
(因为‘lib’没有被指定)
程序包‘ISOcodes’打开成功，MD5和检查也通过
程序包‘fastmatch’打开成功，MD5和检查也通过
程序包‘stopwords’打开成功，MD5和检查也通过
程序包‘quanteda’打开成功，MD5和检查也通过

下载的二进制程序包在
	C:\Users\cathy\AppData\Local\Temp\RtmpiMimAv\downloaded_packages里
警告: 程序包‘tidytext’是用R版本4.4.2 来建造的
警告: 程序包‘quanteda’是用R版本4.4.2 来建造的
